# Wiki Module

## Overview

Wiki module provides project-scoped knowledge base with multi-level directory tree, raw resource import, and markdown editing

## Goals

- **G1** — Wiki module provides project-scoped knowledge base with multi-level directory tree, raw resource import, and markdown editing
- **G2** — Wiki Search & Tagging System provides VitePress/VSCode-style context-aware full-text search

## Key Architecture Decisions

- **A1** — Wiki Knowledge Layer Architecture

## Key Designs

- **D1** — Wiki Knowledge Layer — Storage, Tree API, Raw Resources, and Agent Tools
- **D2** — Wiki Frontend — Tree Navigation, Raw Import, and Tab Integration

## Module Dependencies

Depends on: [project](project/module.ad)

